quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,8,"Joomi amen, naaduɓe ka Aljannaaji ñiiɓal, ɗin ɗi poduɗaa ɓe, e kala moƴƴuɗo e baabiraaɓe maɓɓe, e genndiraaɓe maɓɓe, e geñngol maɓɓe. Pellet, ko Aan woni pooluɗo, Ñeeñɗo Oon."
  40,9,"Daɗndaaɓe [kuuɗe] e bonɗe ɗen. Kala mo daɗnduɗaa [kuuɗe] mum bonɗe ɗen nden Ñande, haray pellet, A yurmiii mo". Ko ɗum woni maloore mawnunde ndeen."
  40,10,"Yedduɓe ɓeen noddiroyte: "Ko tikkere Allah nden ɓuri mawnude, e dii ko tikkanɗon ko'e mon ɗum, tuma noddetenoɗon e gooŋɗinal, njeddon."
  40,11,"Ɓe mbi'a: "Joomi amen, A warii min laawi ɗiɗi, nguurnuɗaa min laawi ɗiɗi: min qirrike bakkaat amen ɗin. Taw si laawol jaltirngol hino woodi?"."
  40,12,""Ɗuum mooɗon, ko tawde si Allah tan noddanooma, on njeddon; si O kafidaama, ngooŋɗinon. Ñaawoore nden ko Allah heeranii, Toowɗo, Mawɗo On"."
  40,13,"Ko Kaŋko woni kolloowo on Ma'andeeji makko ɗin, o jippinirana on toɓo ka kammu. Kono taskotaako, si wonaa nduttotooɗo [e Allah]."
  40,14,"Rewiree Allah, laɓɓinirangol mo diina kan, hay si he'eferɓe ɓeen njɗaa."
  40,15,"Ko o toowuɗo darjaaji, Jeyɗo Arsi kin. Homo jippiniria wahayu oon, yamiroore makko, e on mo o muuyani e jiyaaɓe makko ɓeen, no o jeertinirde ñalnde Kawral ngal,"
  40,16,"ñande ɓe feeñoyta. Hu'unde suuɗotaako Allah, e fee maɓɓe. Ko hommbo laamu woodani hannde? Ko Allah Bajjo, pooluɗo On."